# Column-at-a-Time projection

## Description

Column subset selection - only read needed columns.

## Implementation

```rust
pub fn column_projection() {
    // Process entire columns at once
    // Excellent cache behavior
    // Sequential I/O
}
```

## Cost Model

- Sequential I/O: fastest possible
- Cache-friendly: process full columns
- SIMD: 4-8x speedup for operations

